OL,6,FOperations involving artificial
OL,7,Fvaginal mesh are still being performed
OL,8,Fat Betsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,9,FBoard even though the procedures were
OL,10,Fpaused by the Welsh Government in 2018.
OL,12,FIn 2018, the Welsh Government
OL,13,Fannounced that TVT and TVT-O
OL,14,Foperations, which involve inserting
OL,15,Fmesh to treat urinary incontinence in
OL,16,Fwomen, would be paused until a set of
OL,17,Fconditions to ensure that patients
OL,18,Freceive safe and high-quality care are
OL,19,Fmet.
