OL,3,C'Paused' mesh operations still being
OL,4,Ccarried out at North Wales Health Board
OL,6,FBut S4C's Y Byd ar Bedwar can reveal
OL,7,Fthat 13 patients have had a TVT
OL,8,Foperation at the Health Board since
OL,9,F2018.
OL,11,FThe programme asked every health board
OL,12,Fin Wales how many TVT or TVT-O
OL,13,Foperations they have performed between
OL,14,F2005-2025, and Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,15,FUniversity Health Board was the only
OL,16,Fone which confirmed patients had
OL,17,Fundergone these treatments since 2018.
