OL,3,C'Paused' mesh operations still being
OL,4,Ccarried out at North Wales Health Board
OL,6,FDr Wael Agur, one of the top
OL,7,Fgynaecologists in Britain, carries out
OL,8,Fprivate work on behalf of the NHS in
OL,9,FScotland and has given evidence in
OL,10,Fseveral legal cases against Betsi
OL,11,FCadwaladr health board which relate to
OL,12,Fvaginal mesh.
OL,14,FResponding to the figures, he said: "I
OL,15,Fam very surprised. I did not expect a
OL,16,Fhealth board in the UK to be using
OL,17,Fmesh procedures for incontinence when
OL,18,Fthere is an ongoing pause since 2018.
OL,19,FI have stopped using mesh for over a
OL,20,Fdecade now.
