OL,3,C'Paused' mesh operations still being
OL,4,Ccarried out at North Wales Health Board
OL,6,F"For 12 years now I've stopped using
OL,7,Fmesh completely, and I have not come
OL,8,Facross any patient where the local
OL,9,Fteam decided that her only option is
OL,10,Fthe mesh for incontinence, the TVT or
OL,11,Fthe TVT-O.
OL,13,F"I don't think this is the right thing
OL,14,Fto do - this is not the right way
OL,15,Fforward. The procedures TVT and TVT-O
OL,16,Fthat are still being used at this
OL,17,Fhealth board are paused for a reason.
OL,18,FAnd the reason is the long term
OL,19,Fdebilitating complications that are
OL,20,Favoidable because there are safer
OL,21,Falternatives."
