OL,3,C'Paused' mesh operations still being
OL,4,Ccarried out at North Wales Health Board
OL,6,FDr Clara Day, BCUHB's Executive
OL,7,FMedical Director, said: "Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment and NICE guidance
OL,9,Fstipulates conservative and well-
OL,10,Fdocumented use of vaginal mesh
OL,11,Fprocedures. In its '2021 exceptional
OL,12,Fsurveillance of urinary incontinence
OL,13,Fand pelvic organ prolapse:
OL,14,Fmanagement', NICE stated TVT-O
OL,15,F(tension-free vaginal tape-obturator):
OL,16,F'should not be offered routinely. In
OL,17,Fthe future, we feel the TVT-O should
OL,18,Fonly be used in exceptional
OL,19,Fcircumstances, if at all.'
