OL,6,F"Since 2018, the health board has not
OL,7,Fundertaken any TVT-O procedures. In
OL,8,Fthe same six-year period, 13 TVT
OL,9,F(tension-free vaginal tape) procedures
OL,10,Fwere completed.
OL,12,F"For management of urodynamically
OL,13,Fproven stress urinary incontinence,
OL,14,Fthe use of TVT is only considered in
OL,15,Fthe context of strict governance
OL,16,Fcontrols.
